Whenever I purchase movies, I do so with the intention of watching them several times.  I am so pleased with the two "Transporter" movies and I know I will watch them until they wear out.  Jason Statham is so smooth  in both movies and, I think, a great actor.  I liked him in "Spy" because his character spoofed the many action roles he normally plays.  I recommend all of the "Transporter movies."
